title: 2015 Women’s Leadership Luncheon hosts largest turnout yet! (United Way of Cass-Clay)
text: ( Source : United Way of Cass-Clay) The 2015 Women 's Leadership Luncheon broke another record in attendance this year with 750 women at the event. United Way was excited to present on the importance of education and why we invest in children
